<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 1.3cm; }
  body {
    font-family: Calibri, 'Gill Sans', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #1A1A2E;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .letter-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #F5A623;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12pt;
  }
  .letter-header img.logo { height: 48px; }
  .letter-header .company { font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; }
  .date { margin-bottom: 12pt; }
  .to-block { margin-bottom: 12pt; }
  .to-block .line { margin: 0 0 2pt 0; }
  .subject { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 12pt; }
  p.body { margin: 0 0 12pt 0; text-align: justify; }
  .section-heading { font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 4pt 0; }
  table.comp {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 12pt;
  }
  table.comp th, table.comp td {
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  table.comp td.amount, table.comp th.amount { text-align: right; }
  table.comp thead th {
    background-color: #F5A623;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 12pt;
  }
  table.comp tbody td { font-size: 11pt; }
  table.comp tr.total td { font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; }
  table.net td { font-weight: bold; font-size: 13pt; }
  ul.documents { margin: 0 0 12pt 0; padding-left: 20px; }
  ul.documents li { margin-bottom: 2pt; }
  .signature { margin-top: 24pt; margin-bottom: 12pt; }
  .signature .name { font-weight: bold; }
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
    padding-top: 6px;
    margin-top: 18pt;
    font-size: 8pt;
    color: #555;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="letter-header">
  <img class="logo" src="btl_logo-withtext.png" alt="Bitloka Solutions">
  <div class="company">Bitloka Solutions Private Limited</div>
</div>

<div class="date">{{ date | default('') }}</div>

<div class="to-block">
  <div class="line">{{ candidate_name | default('') }}</div>
  <div class="line">{{ candidate_address | default('') }}</div>
  <div class="line">{{ candidate_email | default('') }} | {{ candidate_phone | default('') }}</div>
</div>

<div class="subject">Re: Offer of Employment</div>

<p class="body">Dear {{ candidate_name | default('') }},</p>

<p class="body">We are pleased to offer you the position of <strong>{{ role | default('') }}</strong>
at Bitloka Solutions Private Limited. We are confident your skills and experience will be a
valuable addition to our team.</p>

{% if internship_acknowledgement %}
<p class="body">{{ internship_acknowledgement }}</p>
{% endif %}

<p class="body">Your annual Cost to Company (CTC) will be
<strong>{{ annual_ctc | default('') }}</strong>, structured as set out in the monthly
compensation breakup below.</p>

<div class="section-heading">Monthly Earnings</div>
<table class="comp">
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Earnings</th><th class="amount">Amount</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Basic Salary</td><td class="amount">{{ basic_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>House Rent Allowance (HRA)</td><td class="amount">{{ hra_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Leave Travel Allowance (LTA)</td><td class="amount">{{ lta_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Work From Home Allowance</td><td class="amount">{{ wfh_allowance_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Flexi Pay</td><td class="amount">{{ flexi_pay_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr class="total"><td>Total Earnings</td><td class="amount">{{ total_earnings_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="section-heading">Monthly Deductions</div>
<table class="comp">
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Deductions</th><th class="amount">Amount</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Professional Tax</td><td class="amount">{{ professional_tax_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>TDS @ 10%</td><td class="amount">{{ tds_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
    <tr class="total"><td>Total Deductions</td><td class="amount">{{ total_deductions_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<table class="comp net">
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Net Monthly Take Home</td><td class="amount">{{ net_take_home_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

{% if business_performance_bonus_pct %}
<div class="section-heading">Performance Bonuses</div>
<p class="body">Business Performance Bonus: Up to {{ business_performance_bonus_pct }}% of total
annual earnings, provisioned in {{ business_performance_bonus_period | default('March/April') }}.</p>
{% if individual_performance_bonus_pct %}
<p class="body">Individual Performance Bonus: Up to {{ individual_performance_bonus_pct }}% of total
annual earnings, provisioned in {{ individual_performance_bonus_period | default('September/October') }}.</p>
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

<p class="body">Either party may terminate this engagement by giving the other written notice of
<strong>eight (8) weeks</strong>.</p>

<div class="section-heading">Terms and Conditions</div>
<p class="body">This offer is subject to your acceptance of the Company's standard terms of
employment, satisfactory completion of background verification, and your continued compliance
with Company policies. Your employment is governed by the laws of India and subject to the
jurisdiction of the courts at Bangalore.</p>

<div class="section-heading">Documents Required</div>
<ul class="documents">
  <li>Government-issued photo identification (Aadhaar / Passport)</li>
  <li>PAN card</li>
  <li>Educational and prior-employment certificates</li>
  <li>Recent passport-size photograph</li>
</ul>

<div class="section-heading">Non-Disclosure</div>
<p class="body">You agree to hold in strict confidence all proprietary and confidential
information of the Company and its clients, both during and after your engagement, and to sign
the Company's Non-Disclosure Agreement on joining.</p>

<p class="body">Please confirm your acceptance of this offer by signing and returning a copy of
this letter. We look forward to welcoming you to Bitloka Solutions.</p>

<div class="signature">
  <div>For Bitloka Solutions Private Limited,</div>
  <br>
  <div class="name">Vishal Honnatti</div>
  <div>Director</div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  #311/1, Zikhin Bhavan, 26th X, BSK II Stage, Bangalore - 560070 |
  www.bitloka.com | contact@bitloka.com
</div>

</body>
</html>
